casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Butler, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Butler (1990), 48 Ohio St. 3d 78.]

(No. 89-164 Submitted December 5, 1989 Decided January 24, 1990.) Robert D. Horowitz, prosecuting attorney, and Ronald Mark Caldwell, for appellee. Randall M. Dana, public defender, and Barbara A. Fambacher, for appellant James Curtis Butler.

This cause is affirmed on authority of State v. Watson (1989), 47 Ohio St. 3d 93, 547 N.E. 2d 1181.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
